{"tid":668861,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel推出中國超級英雄系列","createTime":"2018-05-18T03:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T05:30:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5a5c670e3bce039080a9593d032a95f2dcf17e","tid":668861,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://imoney.hket.com/article/2073548?r=cpsdfb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimoney.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2073548%3Fr%3Dcpsdfb&d=4RKMSrBp3%2BDoZuM3FwVM1r%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=04634177\" target=\"_blank\">http://imoney.hket.com/article/2073548?r=cpsdfb</a><br />\n<br />\n官方認證 Marvel出中國版英雄<br />\n<br />\n19:23 2018/05/15<br />\n<br />\n已上映一段時間的《復仇者聯盟3》（復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰），破各地票房紀錄，掀起Marvel熱潮。Marvel推出多個超級英雄，在全球獲得大批Fans。近日Marvel Universe更擴展至中國，Marvel與內地漫畫家合作，推出首批國產超級英雄。<br />\n<br />\n早前，Marvel 宣布與網易（內地最大遊戲及科技公司之一）合作，推出只屬於中國的超級英雄。與Marvel合作的兩部漫畫《三皇鬥戰士》及《氣旋》已在上周三（9日）正式在《網易漫畫》上線連載。<br />\n<br />\n《三皇鬥戰士》及《氣旋》這兩部漫畫以中國文化為主題，會有內地漫畫家及編劇參與創作。而漫威漫畫主編CB Cebulski曾在法新社的採訪中指，這些超級英雄會具有濃厚的中國文化色彩，並把角色設在現實世界。<br />\n<br />\n有網民表示，也許會有機會可以和《復仇者聯盟》的英雄一起戰鬥。但Marvel並沒有提及中國版超級英雄會否出現在《復仇者聯盟》或其他Marvel系列中出現或客串。<br />\n<br />\nThe Economist Corporate Network總監Robert Koepp告訴BBC，這可以幫助Marvel擴展中國市埸，迪士尼一定認為中國有巨大且未經開發的市埸潛力。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：黃敏儀"},{"pid":"d1963fef84017b34d2e2cf9f3d216634749172a0","tid":668861,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3edf0e43d573e9b0f1ab20449e17093f804d56e","tid":668861,"uid":147001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果佢加左中國英雄入mcu 我諗我會棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4722a6457a01912b97b6475039526cf57c9cb7c9","tid":668861,"uid":30055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3edf0e43d573e9b0f1ab20449e17093f804d56e","tid":668861,"uid":147001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果佢加左中國英雄入mcu 我諗我會棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"中國隊長大戰英國隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e64029d0603971cd26068bb92094a9a34fadfc5","tid":668861,"uid":15205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:16:21.000Z","msg":"隻手射出麵條"},{"pid":"6a56d3c260412145240897017e59e07386a349f5","tid":668861,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/614wpoAmb4L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F614wpoAmb4L.jpg&h=0692fa78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/china-underground.com/w